{
  "stem": "11067.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we were sitting in the compartment, and oh, of course mother had-- I was also to meet-- my aunt from Holland was also going to see me before I left the country.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my mother had given me a few pieces of jewelry that had been left to give to this aunt in the hopes that she would be able to trade for food, shall we say, or for anything they needed.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because she, this aunt had been joined by another sister, also with children.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The one from Frankfurt had gone to Holland hoping that they would be safer there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we rode on the train all day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We did not see-- I didn't see anybody on the train as far as chaperones.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I do know that they were supposed to be on the train because there were chaperones who came with us but had to return to Germany.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was a stipulation.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "If they did not return, the transports would stop.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And so we were almost in Holland, and suddenly my name was called out that my luggage was to be examined.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Whether it was because this aunt had to get permission to go on the train or whether it was just random, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "However, I had to hide those few pieces of jewelry.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that's why I told you in the beginning that my mother had bought me the pen, because that became a little hiding place.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Remember, I was eight years old.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I still say I was eight going on 45 at that point.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I took out the pen and I dropped the necklace into the little case and put the pen back in neatly.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
